  rcases l with ( _ | ⟨ x0, _ | ⟨ x1, _ | ⟨ x2, _ | ⟨ x3, _ | ⟨ x4, _ | ⟨ x5, _ | ⟨ x6, _ | ⟨ x7, _ | l ⟩ ⟩ ⟩ ⟩ ⟩ ⟩ ⟩ ⟩ ) <;> simp +decide [ List.Perm.swap ];
  unfold CAS; simp +decide [ List.Perm.swap ] ;
